<item>
            <title>[CXF-8296] Custom Boolean ParamConverter wrong behaviour</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-8296</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Attachmente files describes an sample application thats use custom boolean ParamConverter used with @BeanParam + @FormParam parameter. Cxf is returning false for&#160;Wrapper Boolean Object even when null is provided as value in converter.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Libs/Impls like resteasy and jersey works correctly returning null for Wrapper Boolean Object.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is this expected or its a bug ? There is some workaround or way to force null without coercing to false when null is provided ?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;apache-tomee-webprofile-8.0.2&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
